   <td>No H1 present in <a href="/content/ryerson/websupport/legacy-templates.html">legacy templates</a><br> </td> 
  </tr>
  <tr>
   <td>Web style guide and <a href="/content/ryerson/websupport/aem-basics/web-style-guide.html">colour palettes</a> available<br> </td> 
   <td>No standard colour palette; user-defined</td> 
  </tr>
